  "title": "(Full-Time) Service Crew",
  "description": "<p><br /><strong>Schedule:</strong> 5-Day Work Week <br /><strong>Earnings Potential:</strong> Up to $3,500 Gross</p><ul><li><p><strong>Welcome & Connect:</strong> Greet every guest with genuine warmth, setting a positive and inviting tone from the first hello.</p></li><li><p><strong>Guide & Recommend:</strong> Master our menu. Confidently share details, tell the stories behind dishes, and help guests find their perfect meal or drink.</p></li><li><p><strong>Deliver Seamlessly:</strong> Ensure timely, accurate service. Coordinate smoothly with kitchen and bar teams to keep the experience flowing.</p></li><li><p><strong>Maintain & Prepare:</strong> Uphold a spotless, welcoming environment. Quickly reset tables to prepare for the next group of guests.</p></li><li><p><strong>Collaborate & Support:</strong> Be a true team player. Work in sync with everyone to ensure the entire operation runs flawlessly.</p></li></ul><p><strong></strong></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
